reviews.review_text:
excellent aud. best aud. of 76-10-01
very good aud. very good show

Gorgeous Aud Can't say enough about the sound on this one. While I'm a big 76 fan, this one didn't necessarily knock my socks off as far as the performance. Some excellent moments to be sure: Scarlet Begonias, HOTW>Slipknot>Franklins and that Dancin' that weaves in and out the second set are all incredible.
- The recording is very slightly distorted in spots, mostly just on the vocals. Tremendous show, even if some of the transitions are a little forced and hokey (notably Ship of Fools > Dancin').
good show This is a decent show , not the best from 76 however but worthy of adding to ones collection. the recording is good and is easy to listen to.
